Package: kpictureframe
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: KDE Plasma 6 picture frame for your desktop
 KPictureFrame displays a user-defined image (PNG, JPG, SVG) on the
 desktop — for personal photos, logos, or QR codes, with drag & drop
 support and live reload when the configuration changes. Supports a
 folder slideshow mode and an ambient glow effect, and is translated
 into German, Spanish and French.
